data.description: Meticulously maintained home in a serene setting offers an open main level floor plan w/an eat-in kitchen, informal dining area and living room that step out onto the back patio. Enjoy the convenience of laundry on the main floor and a primary bedroom with it's own ensuite bath and walk-in closet. The second floor offers two additional bedrooms, a loft space, and a full bath. Ample windows allow for tons of natural light.
